LLM-Based Code Editor

Overview

This project is an AI-powered code editor that integrates a Large Language Model (LLM) to provide intelligent code suggestions, auto-completions, and real-time debugging assistance. The editor enhances the coding experience by leveraging natural language processing to understand and improve code.

Features

AI-Powered Code Suggestions: Get real-time recommendations for completing and optimizing code.

Syntax Highlighting: Supports multiple programming languages with syntax-aware formatting.

Auto-Completion: Suggests relevant functions, variables, and structures based on the context.

Real-Time Debugging: Identifies potential issues and suggests fixes.

Natural Language Commands: Interact with the editor using plain English queries.

Customizable Themes: Adjust the UI for a personalized coding experience.

Extensible Plugin System: Allows users to add additional functionalities.
